if you want a bigger paycheck , read this book ! i owe my latest payday to jack chapman 's negotiating strategies . my newest employer aimed pretty low for their first offer , lower than what i had made at my last job , considering all of the skills and experience i was bringing to the table . but by applying some of the techniques in the book , i was able to get 22 % more money . i 've never negotiated my salary before : i was just glad someone thought enough of my skills to make me an offer . now , i know better